Privacy Policy
Information We Collect

Server Events: The Bot logs welcome and farewell messages when members join or leave the server.
User Data: The Bot does not collect, store, or share any personal information from users.
How We Use Information
The information logged by the Bot is used solely to provide the service of announcing member arrivals and departures in your Discord server.

Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not share, sell, or disclose your data to third parties.
The Bot does not collect any personally identifiable information that would need to be shared.
Data Security
We strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your data, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about these Terms of Service or the Privacy Policy, please contact us at nours.mc@outlook.fr.
